    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically sound E46 M3, featuring the legendary S54B32 3.2L inline-six with its signature individual throttle bodies and high-pressure VANOS system. This example delivers linear power delivery up to its 8,000 RPM redline, paired with a tactile 6-speed manual gearbox. The chassis remains taut, benefiting from documented rear subframe reinforcement and refreshed suspension bushings. Equipped with the factory M-Variable Differential Lock, the lateral dynamics and turn-in response are precise. While showing minor aesthetic patina consistent with a well-maintained driver, the powertrain remains robust with consistent compression across all cylinders. A turn-key performance icon for the purist.",
      "price": 34500.0,
