      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Up for sale is a meticulously cared-for vehicle that strikes the perfect balance between luxury and daily utility. The exterior retains a deep, lustrous finish, showing only the minor, expected signs of careful road use, while the body panels remain straight and free of significant blemishes. Inside, the cabin is a testament to pride of ownership; the premium upholstery is clean and supple, and the dashboard remains free of cracks or sun damage. Every feature, from the responsive infotainment system to the ice-cold climate control and power-adjustable seating, operates flawlessly. Mechanically, this car is in excellent health. It has been maintained strictly according to the manufacturer\u2019s schedule, with a comprehensive folder of service records included. The engine delivers smooth, consistent power, the transmission shifts are crisp, and the suspension provides a quiet, composed ride. With plenty of life left on the tires and brakes, this vehicle is truly turn-key and ready for its next owner to enjoy immediately.",
